  "texts": [
    "To illustrate, the prior SOTA prompting-based method, DIN-SQL+GPT-4, reports approximately 60 seconds of inference time per sample on the Spider dataset.",
    "In contrast, our SFT CodeS demonstrates significantly improved efficiency.",
    "The inference times for the 1B, 3B, 7B, and 15B variants are only 0.6, 0.9, 1.1, and 1.5 seconds respectively on the same dataset.",
    "This highlights the superior speed of our models.",
    "In addition to its efficiency, CodeS is also suitable for real-world deployment."
